两名火神山建设者被代收隔离费，当地回应了。
Two Fire Goddess Mountain builders were charged isolation fees, and the local responded.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 蒋子文据微信公众号“秀美浠水”消息，浠水县新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控指挥部3月7日发布《关于我县洗马镇代收“火神山”参建人员隔离期间隔离费用的情况说明》称，近日，浠水县洗马镇两名参建武汉“火神山”医院的建设者，在网上发布返乡后的集中隔离费用证明图片，各大媒体纷纷转发，引起网民广泛关注。
It is indicated that the construction personnel of these hospitals in these days are advised to report the evidence of the cost of these activities on the Internet. These photos have been forwarded by the media and have attracted the attention of the netizens.
县委、县政府高度重视，迅速成立由县纪委、县委宣传部、县公安局组成的联合调查组。
County Party committees and county governments attach great importance to the rapid establishment of county disciplinary committees, county publicity departments, county public security offices composed of joint investigation teams.
经调查，洗马镇政府代收劳务公司隔离费用的情况属实，行为是错误的，反映浠水县执行疫情防控政策不严、作风不实，我们深感自责和愧疚。
After investigation it is true that the segregation fee of these companies is true and that it is wrong to reflect the lax implementation of the disease prevention and control policy and the improper style of behavior in these counties. We deeply regret and remorse.
该笔代收费用已于3月7日上午退还劳务公司，并向当事人道歉。
The charge was returned to the company on the morning of March 7 and the party apologized.
对此，我们对各媒体单位和广大网民的关心、关注、监督、支持表示真诚的感谢，同时就有关事项说明如下：浠水县洗马镇参建“两山”医院人员岑某和王某于2020年2月21日从武汉返浠，按照疫情防控相关要求，两人返浠后安排到县“不见不散”宾馆集中隔离点隔离14天。
It is suggested that these two individuals should remain in isolation for 14 days following their return to climate change due to the fact that they have returned to the climate change area from Wuhan on February 21, 2020. It is suggested that these two people should be separated from each other for 14 days after returning to their homes due to the epidemic situation.
两人在参建期间，中建三局已比照国家法定假日工资标准支付相关报酬。
The two men in the construction period, China Construction Bureau has been the national statutory holiday pay standards to pay the relevant remuneration.
同时，中建三局另按照每人每天300元的标准发放隔离补贴费用，按照15天计算，每人共计发放4500元。
At the same time, China Construction Bureau will also pay the isolation subsidy according to the standard of 300 yuan per person per day, calculated on the basis of 15 days, a total of 4,500 yuan.
洗马镇在两人隔离期间按照每人每天150元标准代收隔离期间食宿等费用，共计代收4200元，其他超出费用由镇政府承担，代收费用由武汉今润世家建筑劳务有限公司直接拨付到洗马镇会计服务中心。
During the period of separation, the town collected 4,200 yuan for board and lodging according to the standard of 150 yuan per person per day, and other expenses were borne by the township government.
3月7日晚，经县委研究决定，对洗马镇负责隔离点工作的党委委员、副镇长马金安同志给予免职处理。
On the night of March 7, Comrade Ma Jinan, deputy mayor and member of the Party committee in charge of the quarantine point in the town of Zima, was dismissed from his post.
我们深刻汲取此次事件的教训，举一反三，进一步查找工作中存在的短板和不足。
We have learned the lessons of this incident, to further find the shortcomings and shortcomings in the work.
经排查，全县其他参加武汉“两山”医院建设的返乡隔离人员，没有向个人收取费用。
After sorting out, the other county participated in Wuhan "two mountains" hospital construction of home quarantine personnel, no individual charges.
对洗马镇其他相关责任人员，将根据调查情况，依纪依法给予严肃处理。
Other responsible personnel in the town will be dealt with seriously according to law and discipline according to the investigation.
再次感谢社会各界、各媒体单位和广大网民的关心和关注，我们坚信，有大家的监督和支持，我们一定能够不断改进工作，严格执行党中央和省、市疫情防控政策要求，打赢疫情防控的人民战争、总体战、阻击战。
We are confident that with your supervision and support, we will be able to improve our work, strictly implement the requirements of the CPC Central Committee and provincial and municipal epidemic prevention and control policies, and win the people's war, the general war and the fight against epidemic diseases.
本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
